  instructions:
  - Welcome! Follow the instructions to complete the back wheel removal task. Use
    Left Controller X button to go Prev and Y button to go Next
  - 'Step 1: Grab the wrench from the tool rack.'
  - 'Step 2: Use the wrench on the left pedal bolt (left in the direction when you
    sit on the bicycle) to loosen it.'
  - 'Step 3: Once loose, grab the pedal and remove it.'
  - 'Step 4: Use the wrench on the right pedal bolt (right in the direction when
    you sit on the bicycle) to loosen it.'
  - 'Step 3: Once loose, grab the pedal and remove it.'
  - Excellent work! You've successfully changed the pedal.
